DTEND:20260402T093000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.589ft at 06:54\n-2.96ft at 09:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\nM
 orning stays on the smaller side\, knee-waist high zone\, then a fresh mix
  of shorter and mid-period NW swell gradually rises\, along with some long
 er-period SSW swell\, during the back half of the day\, setting up thigh-w
 aist-stomach high waves\, showing most size late. Nice early morning tide 
 push. Tide sensitive spots slowed by mid day high.  \n\nLight+ to periodic
 ally low-end moderate N winds through the day for offshore conditions in t
 own. 
