BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260403T065400
DTEND:20260403T103000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.102ft at 06:54\n-2.947ft at 10:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Nice blend of NW swell and longer-period SSW/S swell is good for waist to 
 chest high surf at better spots in the morning\, tapering off a bit over t
 he afternoon. Incoming tide push helps much of the morning\, then the high
 er mid day tide bogs down tide sensitive spots some. \n\nLight\, primarily
  offshore winds in the morning\, shift to a light+ SW sea breeze for the a
 fternoon. 
END:VEVENT
