DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.002ft at 07:24\n-2.95ft at 11:36\n\nOBSERVATION:\nA
  fair size blend of steeper-angled\, selective SSW/S swell rolls in\, as s
 horter-period NW swell fades. Good southerly exposures are thigh-waist hig
 h+\, while focal points see better sets on the morning tide. \n\nLight win
 ds due all day\, offshore most of the morning\, SW sea breeze in the after
 noon. 
